          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Hath Not a Jew Hands? <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue8/stephen_wilson/bio.php" class="link3">Stephen Wilson</a></span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
          <td><img src="/images/spacer.gif" width="1" height="23" border="0" alt=""></td>
